data.title: 270 Long Shore Way, Newnan, GA 30265
data.meta_description: Zillow has 69 photos of this $649,900 6 beds, 4 baths, 3,906 Square Feet single family home located at 270 Long Shore Way, Newnan, GA 30265 built in 2006. MLS #10351459.
data.text: Immaculate home in the beautiful Lake Zachary subdivision with 6 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms. Master bedroom with his and her walk-ins and beautiful barn doors along with a custom shower/tub and heated floors in the master bath. Main level has a guest suite with acrylic walk-in shower attached. Fully upgraded custom kitchen with floor to ceiling cabinets and under mounted lighting. Breakfast nook opens to the spacious living room with custom built in bookcases and stone fireplace. Upstairs are 3 additional bedrooms with the possibility of an office. Gigantic basement has been partially finished with additional bedroom, full bathroom and an office or craft/hobby room and tons of additional storage space. Unfinished portion of the basement is already plumbed for additional bathroom/kitchen. The backyard is an oasis with an expansive back porch which is perfect for entertaining guests and a beautiful setting surrounding the salt water pool. Privacy and luxury are available in this home which has a large lot and woods located on 2 sides. Perfect location is nearby to Peachtree City and Newnan with quick access to the interstate.
